Finally, we compare the effectiveness of mobility restrictions versus mass immunization. The first, is implemented by long distance travel restrictions, a measure already adopted world-wide, throughout 2020, during the COVID-19 pandemic, and with notable results45,46. In GHPM, this restriction is obtained by reducing the travel distance parameter \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
